  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK546">
<l>vēlaṉṟu veṉṟi taruvatu maṉṉavaṉ </l>
<l> kōlatu kōṭā ṉeṉiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is not the javelin that gives victory, but the king's sceptre, if it do no injustice.</l>
            </lg>
